name: prephenate dehydrogenase
classes: Acting on the CH-CH group of donors;
With NAD+ or NADP+ as acceptor
comment: This enzyme in the enteric bacteria also possesses chorismate mutase activity (EC 5.4.99.5 chorismate mutase) and converts chorismate into prephenate.

references.title: Tyrosine biosynthesis in Aerobacter aerogenes. Purification and properties of chorismate mutase-prephenate dehydrogenase.
